## Step 3 — Launch Backend

```bash
cd "c:\Users\Admin\Desktop\HR Project\backend"

# Install dependencies (first time only)
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Start FastAPI on port 8001
uvicorn app.main:app --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8001 --reload
```

**Confirm it's running** — open in browser:
```
http://localhost:8001/docs
```
You should see the Swagger UI with `/api/candidates/{id}`, `/api/interview/start`, and `/ws/interview/{id}`.

---

## Step 4 — Launch Frontend

```bash
cd "c:\Users\Admin\Desktop\HR Project\frontend"

# Install dependencies (first time only)
npm install

# Start Next.js dev server on port 3000
npm run dev
```

Open: `http://localhost:3000`

