## Step 5 — Navigate to the Interview Page

```
http://localhost:3000/interview/TEST-AHMAD-001
```

The page will:
1. Fetch candidate data from `GET /api/candidates/TEST-AHMAD-001`
2. Show registration context panel with Ahmad's form data
3. Display the green **Start** button (microphone icon)

