## Step 6 — Test Scenarios

Click **Start** and wait for Sarah's opening greeting to play (in Jordanian Arabic).

---

### Scenario A — Honest Candidate (Baseline)

Say exactly what's in the contract. Sarah's credibility score should stay near 100.

> 🎤 "أهلاً سارة، اسمي أحمد. عندي 3 سنين خبرة، والراتب اللي بتوقعه 800 دينار."

**Expected behavior**: Sarah asks a follow-up experience question, score stays at 100, no inconsistency logged.

---

### Scenario B — The Lie (Fact Integrity Test)

Deliberately contradict the contract. Sarah's [_verify_facts_node](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/HR%20Project/backend/app/core/interview_agent.py#194-228) should catch this if Sarah herself says the wrong number, OR a `detected_inconsistency` should be logged if the user's claim differs from the contract.

> 🎤 "والله أنا عندي 10 سنين خبرة في هالمجال."

**Expected behavior**:
- If Sarah's *response* repeats "10 years" → [verify_facts](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/HR%20Project/backend/app/core/interview_agent.py#194-228) corrects it back to "3 سنوات" and logs a `llm_hallucination` inconsistency.
- The [credibility_score](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/HR%20Project/backend/app/services/credibility_scorer.py#214-227) drops −10 points.
- After the interview ends, Supabase `interviews.recommendation` should show **"يحتاج تحقق إضافي"** (needs verification).

---

### Scenario C — Persona / Language Test

Switch to English or Formal Arabic (فصحى) to trigger Sarah's dialect enforcement.

> 🎤 (English) "Hello Sarah, my name is Ahmad and I have 3 years of experience."

> 🎤 (فصحى) "مرحباً سارة، لديّ ثلاث سنوات من الخبرة في هذا المجال."

**Expected behavior**: Sarah responds **entirely in Jordanian Arabic** with informal pronouns (شو، ليش، كيفك، والله). If she slips into `لديّ` or English, the [PersonaEnforcer](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/HR%20Project/backend/app/core/persona_enforcer.py#11-134) catches and corrects it before the TTS call.

---

## Step 7 — Supabase Verification Queries

Run after finishing an interview:

```sql
-- Check interview record was created and scored
SELECT
    id,
    status,
    started_at,
    completed_at,
    duration_seconds,
    credibility_score,
    credibility_level,
    recommendation,
    summary,
    jsonb_array_length(transcript)  AS transcript_turns,
    jsonb_array_length(detected_inconsistencies) AS inconsistency_count
FROM interviews
ORDER BY created_at DESC
LIMIT 5;

-- Inspect transcript detail
SELECT
    id,
    jsonb_pretty(transcript) AS transcript_pretty
FROM interviews
ORDER BY created_at DESC
LIMIT 1;
```

---

## Quick Troubleshooting

| Symptom | Likely Cause | Fix |
|---------|-------------|-----|
| `404` on `/api/candidates/TEST-AHMAD-001` | Row not inserted or RLS blocking | Verify SQL insert ran; use Service Role Key |
| `WebSocket Connection Failed` | Backend not running or wrong port | Check `uvicorn` is on `8001`; check `NEXT_PUBLIC_WS_URL` |
| `Contract integrity check failed` | Hash mismatch in [verify_integrity()](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/HR%20Project/backend/app/core/fact_contract.py#56-75) | Should be auto-generated; restart the backend to clear LangGraph state |
| Sarah speaks English | [PersonaEnforcer](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/HR%20Project/backend/app/core/persona_enforcer.py#11-134) not catching it | Check `OPENAI_API_KEY` is loaded; check LangGraph is using [enforce_persona](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/HR%20Project/backend/app/core/interview_agent.py#229-250) node |
| No audio from Sarah | ElevenLabs key missing or quota exceeded | Verify `ELEVENLABS_API_KEY`; check ElevenLabs dashboard for quota |
| `row-level security` error in logs | Using `anon` key instead of service role | Switch `SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY` in [.env](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/HR%20Project/.env) |
